Install first composer:
$ sudo pacman -S composer --noconfirm

Download laravel installer using composer:
$ composer global require "laravel/installer"

Edit ~/.bashrc and place the following line

export PATH=${PATH}:/home/pablolserver/.config/composer/vendor/laravel/installer

for the new configuration to work, execute the following command: (This did not work with me)

sourse ~/.bashrc

Font: 
https://www.trabalhosgratuitos.com/Exatas/Inform%C3%A1tica/Como-Instalar-o-Laravel-no-Arch-Linux-1192958.html

